*.log
*.log.*
*.LOG
logs/
**/logs/
sensor.log
frontend.log
front.log
zero.log
sensor_*.log
build.log
test.log
debug.log
error.log
*.log
*.log.[0-9]
*.log.[0-9][0-9]
nohup.out
.DS_Store

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Markdown Documentation (except README)
